Package: performance.gov
Title: R Client for Performance.gov CX/HISP Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Scrapeable", email = "support@scrapeable.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Access U.S. federal Customer Experience (CX) and High Impact Service
    Provider (HISP) data from Performance.gov. Provides functions to retrieve
    service provider details, CX survey results, and quarterly collection
    summaries as typed tibbles.
